QVC Network Inc said itsagreement in principle with Safeguard Scientifics Inc &lt;SFE>allows Safeguard to name the majority of QVC's directors onlyif a seven mln dlr indebtedness to Safeguard is in default.    Yesterday, QVC said announced it entered into the agreementin principle with Safegaurd under which QVC would receive 13mln dlrs in financing, including seven mln dlrs of QVC notes tobe purchase by Safeguard and a six-mln-dlr revolving creditfacility to be provided by a local bank.    QVC said as long as the seven mln dlr indebtedness toSafeguard remains outstanding, Safeguard will be able to namethree of QVC's nine directors. Safeguard's ability to name amajority of QVC's directors will be triggered only if the sevenmln dlr indebtedness to Safeguard is in default, the companysaid. Reuter&#3;